# Database Conventions

- All tenant-scoped tables include `tenantId` with `@@index([tenantId])`
- Use `@id @default(cuid())` for string IDs
- Include `createdAt` and `updatedAt` on all models
- RLS policies enforced at application layer + PostgreSQL RLS where deployed
- Financial tables require audit trail via `AuditLog` model
